-- Geithner to attend Eurogroup meeting this week
-- 
-- Mon Sep 12, 2011 7:49pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/09/12/us-eurozone-geithner-idUSTRE78B5RK20110912

 

 BRUSSELS  (Reuters) - United States Treasury Secretary Timothy Geithner is to attend part of an informal meeting of euro zone finance ministers on Friday in Poland, euro zone officials said on Monday. 

 "He should be attending part of the Eurogroup," said one euro zone official, who asked not to be named. Two other officials involved in the preparation of the meeting in the south-western city of Wroclaw confirmed Geithner was to attend. (Reporting by  Jan Strupczewski , Editing by Chizu Nomiyama)